# Phase 7: Preview Deployments

**Phase:** 7 of 12
**Status:** Not Started
**Depends on:** Phase 3 (GitHub App -- installation tokens, webhook routing), Phase 4 (Build system -- image building pipeline), Phase 5 (Deployment engine -- Deployer, PortAllocator, CaddyClient), Phase 6 (Webhook handler foundation -- signature validation, event parsing)
**Depended on by:** Phase 8 (may enhance preview deployments with build caching optimizations), Phase 9+ (dashboard preview deployment UI enhancements)

---

## Goal

Every pull request gets a live preview URL at `pr-{N}--{slug}.yourdomain.dev`. Preview containers start when a PR is opened or updated, rebuild on new commits, and clean up automatically when the PR is closed or merged. GitHub shows commit status checks (pending/success/failure) on each commit, and a bot posts or updates a single PR comment with the preview link.

After this phase:
- Opening a PR triggers an automatic preview build and deployment
- Pushing new commits to a PR branch rebuilds and re-deploys the preview
- The preview is accessible at `pr-{N}--{slug}.yourdomain.dev`
- GitHub shows a commit status check linking to the preview URL
- A bot comment on the PR contains the live preview link, build status, and build time
- Closing or merging a PR stops the preview container, releases the port, removes the Caddy route, and deletes preview Docker images
- Preview deployments use the "preview" scope environment variables
- Preview images are not counted toward the 10-image retention limit

---

## Architecture Context

```
GitHub (PR event)               Dashboard                     Core
  |                                |                            |
  |-- POST /api/webhooks/github -->|                            |
  |                                |-- verify HMAC-SHA256       |
  |                                |-- parse pull_request event |
  |                                |-- handleWebhook(ctx) ----->|
  |                                |                            |
  |                                |              [opened/synchronize/reopened]
  |                                |                            |-- create deployment record
  |                                |                            |    (type=preview, prNumber=N)
  |                                |                            |-- setCommitStatus(pending)
  |<-- 200 { received: true } ----|<----------------------------|
  |                                |                            |
  |                                |              [async build pipeline]
  |                                |                            |-- clone repo (PR head SHA)
  |                                |                            |-- build Docker image
  |                                |                            |    tag: {project}:pr-{N}-{sha}
  |                                |                            |-- allocate port (4000-4999)
  |                                |                            |-- start container
  |                                |                            |-- health check
  |                                |                            |-- CaddyClient.addRoute()
  |                                |                            |    pr-{N}--{slug}.domain -> :port
  |                                |                            |-- update deployment record
  |                                |                            |-- setCommitStatus(success, previewUrl)
  |                                |                            |-- createOrUpdatePRComment()
  |                                |                            |
  |                                |              [closed/merged]
  |                                |                            |-- stop preview container
  |                                |                            |-- PortAllocator.release(port)
  |                                |                            |-- CaddyClient.removeRoute()
  |                                |                            |-- delete preview Docker images
  |                                |                            |-- update deployment status=archived
```

### URL Routing Detail

```
Request: https://pr-42--myapp.yourdomain.dev
         |
         v
Cloudflare DNS: *.yourdomain.dev -> VPS IP
         |
         v
Caddy (VPS):
  pr-42--myapp.yourdomain.dev {
      reverse_proxy localhost:4001
  }
         |
         v
Docker container: myapp:pr-42-a1b2c3d (port 4001)
```

---

## Environment Variables Required

No new environment variables are introduced in this phase. The following must already be available from prior phases:

| Variable | Source | Used By |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `GITHUB_APP_ID` | Phase 3 | Obtaining installation tokens for API calls |
| `GITHUB_APP_PRIVATE_KEY` | Phase 3 | JWT signing for installation auth |
| `PLATFORM_DOMAIN` | Phase 1 | `generatePreviewUrl()` in `url.ts` |
| `CADDY_ADMIN_URL` | Phase 5 | CaddyClient for route management |
| `DATABASE_URL` | Phase 2 | Deployment records, port allocations |

